OL,3,CNorthern Ireland reacts to
OL,4,Cchancellor's Spring Statement
OL,6,FStormont's finance minister says
OL,7,Fpublic services have been "put to the
OL,8,Fbottom of the pile" in the
OL,9,Fchancellor's Spring Statement.
OL,11,FJohn O'Dowd was speaking after Rachel
OL,12,FReeves outlined the plan in the House
OL,13,Fof Commons on Wednesday, announcing
OL,14,Fshe was cutting the universal credit
OL,15,Fhealth element and freezing it until
OL,16,F2030.
