OL,6,FThe changes came as the Office for
OL,7,FBudget Responsibility found the
OL,8,Fpackage of benefit cuts announced last
OL,9,Fweek would not raise as much money as
OL,10,Fthe government hoped.
OL,12,FIn her statement on changes to the
OL,13,Fpublic finances, Reeves announced
OL,14,Fsignificant cuts in spending but
OL,15,Fconfirmed there will be no tax rises.
OL,17,FSinn Fein minister John O'Dowd said:
OL,18,F"While our public services are crying
OL,19,Fout for investment the new Westminster
OL,20,FGovernment is continuing the austerity
OL,21,Fagenda of the previous government.
