OL,3,CNorthern Ireland reacts to
OL,4,Cchancellor's Spring Statement
OL,6,F"Instead of prioritising investment in
OL,7,Fpublic services the Westminster
OL,8,FGovernment has decided to invest
OL,9,F#2.2bn in a renewed arms race when
OL,10,Fwhat we actually need is more doctors,
OL,11,Fnurses, teachers and homes for
OL,12,Ffamilies and workers to live in. We
OL,13,Fneed investment in people and
OL,14,Fcommunities not more arms and
OL,15,Fausterity.
OL,17,F"While the Westminster Government
OL,18,Ftoday announced #14m of new funding
OL,19,Fthis will not meet the many
OL,20,Fsignificant pressures on our budgets.
