OL,3,CNorthern Ireland reacts to
OL,4,Cchancellor's Spring Statement
OL,6,F"From next week local businesses will
OL,7,Fface increased bills following the
OL,8,Fhike in National Insurance
OL,9,Fcontributions previously imposed by
OL,10,FWestminster however, they will be left
OL,11,Fdisappointed again by the lack of
OL,12,Finvestment by the Chancellor.
OL,14,F"The public sector will also incur
OL,15,Fadditional costs for increased
OL,16,FNational Insurance contributions. The
OL,17,Ffunding that will be provided for this
OL,18,Fwill fall far short of what is needed."
