OL,3,CNorthern Ireland reacts to
OL,4,Cchancellor's Spring Statement
OL,6,FDUP MP Sammy Wilson described the
OL,7,FSpring Statement as a "missed
OL,8,Fopportunity".
OL,10,FHe said: "Instead of taking the
OL,11,Fopportunity to restore business
OL,12,Fconfidence and chart a new course, the
OL,13,Fchancellor has doubled down on
OL,14,Fpolicies that stifle enterprise and
OL,15,Fburden working people.
OL,17,F"The decision to raise employers'
OL,18,FNational Insurance contributions was
OL,19,Falways destined to damage business
OL,20,Fconfidence and harm our economy.
